    "For top generation PC-JeDi has a notably lower FPND and W P 1 scores than MPGAN yet performs worse in W M 1 and W EFP 1.",
    "The metrics Cov and MMD are essentially saturated by all models, as they are in agreement with the upper limit defined by the natural variation in the MC samples.",
    "Some of the values seem to be in tension with visual inspection.",
    "Most notably, W P 1 for gluon jets suggests PC-JeDi with the EM solver outperforms MPGAN, despite the observed underestimation at low values of p rel T for the three leading constituent.",
